window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p>Audible presents <i>The Opposite of Love</i>, an Audible Original. Dheeman, a travel influencer, lives an enviable life full of paid-for travel and every luxury one can dream about. Amal, on the other hand, has just about scraped enough money for her first international flight. When the two of them meet on a long-haul flight to the US, they are immediately drawn to each other despite their difference. Over the air miles they rack up, secrets start to stumble out. It turns out their meeting wasn't accidental but orchestrated. Their pasts are intertwined, and while one's looking for redemption, the other's looking for revenge. Falling in love doesn't figure on their list, but when has it ever?</p> <p>Disclaimer: the show is for adult listeners and contains expletives, strong language and mature content including intimate scenes that support the storyline. This is a work of fiction, and any resemblance to real persons (dead or alive), places and/or events is purely co-incidental. This show does not endorse, promote, encourage or support the use or consumption of any type of drugs, alcohol or tobacco products. This show audiobook is not intended to outrage, insult, defame or wound or hurt any religion or the religious sentiments, belief or feelings of any person, entity, class or community or to denigrate any institution or person, living or dead. Listener’s discretion is strongly advised.</p>"; 
